profile:
We service Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Markham, Newmarket, Bradford, Aurora, North York, Scarborough, Pickering, Ajax, Whitby, Oshawa, Bowmanville, Courtice, Mississauga, Etobicoke and Brampton.

Locally owned, we specialize in all major and minor home repairs. Our uniformed techs are bonded, fully insured and our work is guaranteed. Let us help with that growing "to do" list. Call today!

Handyman Services, Bathroom & Kitchen - Fixtures and Accessories, Fences & Gates, Gutters and Eaves-troughs, Moldings / Moudings, Dry Wall Contractors, Tile and Grout Cleaning, Windows & Doors, Paint & Wallpaper Contractors.

profile: Home Best Solutions is a family owned business with over 20 years of collective experience in construction, architectural, renovation and project management. We specialize in remodeling and creating custom solutions for our customer's homes and office area. We truly understand that your house is more than a home, so our team is dedicated to our customer's needs and exceeding their expectations. Our exceptional level for customer service, attention to detail and workmanship sets us apart from the competition. Home Best Solutions values professionalism, client-focused interactions, and efficiency. We look forward to working with you!
